history.content:
Hey all,

We are recruiting problem writers for Berkeley Math Tournament (BMT), which holds biannual student-run math contests for middle and high schoolers. Our mission is to share mathematics with students from the Bay Area and beyond through exciting math problems. If you are interested in writing math problems, playing games, and making friends who like math and math contests, we invite you to check us out! Please fill out the following form if you want to learn more: https://forms.gle/CwEQYVJr8xbd4s41A
history.subject: Join Problem Writing at Berkeley Math Tournament!
